00:43:04,000 --> 00:43:06,640
They're just
supposed to be creative.

544
00:43:09,800 --> 00:43:13,440
So, what do you want to be
when you grow up?

545
00:43:13,840 --> 00:43:17,360
I don't know.
I want to go on adventures, I think.

546
00:43:17,480 --> 00:43:20,280
Not get stuck in one place.
How about you?

547
00:43:22,560 --> 00:43:26,000
Go on adventures, too.
Not get stuck, too.

548
00:43:26,120 --> 00:43:28,880
Anyway, we can't
predict the exact future.

549
00:43:29,800 --> 00:43:30,840
That's true.

550
00:43:33,440 --> 00:43:36,400
It's possible I may
wet the bed, by the way. Later, I mean.

