00:43:52,480 --> 00:43:53,840
It's not
an accomplishment button.

558
00:43:53,920 --> 00:43:55,800
I inherited it from my mother.

559
00:43:56,400 --> 00:43:59,640
It's not actually meant for a male to
wear, but I don't give a damn.

