00:44:01,920 --> 00:44:03,800
Are your foster parents
still mad at you,

561
00:44:03,880 --> 00:44:05,760
for getting in trouble so much?

562
00:44:06,120 --> 00:44:08,160
I don't think so.

563
00:44:08,240 --> 00:44:10,240
We're starting to get to
know each other better.

564
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:12,320
I feel I'm in
a real family now.

565
00:44:12,400 --> 00:44:14,320
Not like yours,
but similar to one.

566
00:44:15,600 --> 00:44:17,920
I always wished
I was an orphan.

