00:46:02,160 --> 00:46:03,200
I like it.

579
00:46:06,000 --> 00:46:07,280
Tilt your head sideways.

580
00:46:15,440 --> 00:46:17,120
You can touch my chest.

581
00:46:19,440 --> 00:46:22,040
I... I think they're
going to grow more.

