00:48:15,360 --> 00:48:17,520
Dear Sam, it saddens
me to write this letter,

596
00:48:17,600 --> 00:48:19,600
but Mrs. Billingsley
and I have decided

597
00:48:19,680 --> 00:48:21,680
we cannot permit you
to return to our home.

598
00:48:21,760 --> 00:48:25,440
I know you mean well.
Do trust me, this is for the best.

599
00:48:25,520 --> 00:48:27,760
Godspeed, Herbert Billingsley.

600
00:48:39,480 --> 00:48:43,960
Be advised, the two of you will
never see each other again.

601
00:48:44,040 --> 00:48:47,920
Those were your last words.
Do you understand?

