00:49:45,880 --> 00:49:48,000
That was one of the
best pitched campsites I've ever seen.

616
00:49:48,080 --> 00:49:49,200
Honestly.

617
00:49:49,280 --> 00:49:50,600
Thank you.

618
00:49:53,760 --> 00:49:56,200
You don't want to be
a Khaki Scout anymore?

