00:53:02,640 --> 00:53:04,080
I hate you.

672
00:53:05,080 --> 00:53:06,400
Don't say "hate."

673
00:53:06,480 --> 00:53:07,920
Why not? I mean it.

674
00:53:08,800 --> 00:53:11,960
You think you mean it,
in this moment. You're trying to hurt me.

675
00:53:12,040 --> 00:53:13,240
Exactly.

676
00:53:14,680 --> 00:53:17,920
I know what you do
