which we didn't do on purpose.

689
00:54:23,680 --> 00:54:27,840
When we first met each other,
something happened to us.

690
00:54:29,440 --> 00:54:30,800
That's very eloquent.

691
00:54:31,440 --> 00:54:33,720
I can't argue against
anything you're saying.

692
00:54:34,360 --> 00:54:37,520
But then again, I don't have to,
'cause you're 12 years old.

693
00:54:39,800 --> 00:54:42,720
Look, let's face it.

694
00:54:44,320 --> 00:54:47,920
You're probably a much more
intelligent person than I am.

695
00:54:48,800 --> 00:54:50,960
In fact, I guarantee it.

696
00:54:51,040 --> 00:54:52,840
But even smart kids
stick their finger

697
00:54:52,920 --> 00:54:54,520
