sockets sometimes.

698
00:54:56,480 --> 00:54:58,880
It takes time to
figure things out.

699
00:54:59,560 --> 00:55:03,120
It's been proven by history.
All mankind makes mistakes.

700
00:55:05,080 --> 00:55:06,440
It's our job to
try to protect you

701
00:55:06,520 --> 00:55:09,720
