dangerous ones, if we can.

702
00:55:09,800 --> 00:55:11,440
You want a slug?

703
00:55:21,760 --> 00:55:23,480
What's your rush?

704
00:55:23,560 --> 00:55:27,160
You've got your whole life
in front of yourself.

705
00:55:27,240 --> 00:55:28,600
Ahead of you, I mean.

706
00:55:28,920 --> 00:55:31,480
Maybe so.
Anyway, you're a bachelor.

