00:55:32,920 --> 00:55:33,960
So are you.

708
00:55:34,040 --> 00:55:35,080
That's true.

709
00:55:37,880 --> 00:55:39,800
Did you love someone ever?

710
00:55:41,960 --> 00:55:43,160
Yes, I did.

711
00:55:43,240 --> 00:55:44,440
What happened?

712
00:55:46,320 --> 00:55:48,000
