719
00:56:48,480 --> 00:56:49,600
I like his girl.

720
00:56:49,680 --> 00:56:50,760
She's too scruffy for me.

721
00:56:50,840 --> 00:56:52,080
Supposedly,
they got to third base.

722
00:56:52,160 --> 00:56:53,640
That's not true.
