723
00:56:53,720 --> 00:56:54,760
Over shirt or under shirt?

724
00:56:56,680 --> 00:56:57,920
Damn us.

725
00:57:01,720 --> 00:57:03,720
It's none of our business.

726
00:57:08,920 --> 00:57:12,920
This troop has been
very shabby to Field Mate Sam Shakusky.

727
00:57:13,000 --> 00:57:15,840
In fact, we've been
a bunch of mean jerks.

728
00:57:19,440 --> 00:57:21,200
Why's he so unpopular?

729
00:57:22,040 --> 00:57:24,560
I admit, supposedly,
he's emotionally disturbed,

730
00:57:24,640 --> 00:57:29,160
but he's also
a disadvantaged orphan. How would you feel?

731
00:57:29,240 --> 00:57:30,320
Nickleby?

732
00:57:31,120 --> 00:57:32,160
Deluca?

733
00:57:32,880 --> 00:57:33,920
Lazy-Eye?

734
00:57:34,400 --> 00:57:35,440
Gadge?

735
00:57:36,120 --> 00:57:39,200
He's a fellow Khaki Scout,
and he needs our help.

736
00:57:39,280 --> 00:57:41,000
Are we man enough to give that

737
00:57:41,120 --> 00:57:44,160
so part of his brain
doesn't get removed out of him?

738
00:57:45,000 --> 00:57:47,720
They were prepared
to die for each other out there.

739
00:57:51,320 --> 00:57:54,960
Okay. Okay. What do you need?

740
00:57:55,040 --> 00:57:56,960
For starters?
Three yards of chicken wire,

741
00:57:57,040 --> 00:57:59,280
some ripped up newspapers,
and a bucket of wheat paste.

742
00:58:26,760 --> 00:58:29,200
In other words, it's over.

743
00:58:29,280 --> 00:58:33,040
I guess so. For the moment.

744
00:58:33,120 --> 00:58:35,400
Until further notice.

745
00:58:35,480 --> 00:58:36,600
That's right.

746
00:58:36,720 --> 00:58:37,720
I understand.

747
00:58:39,280 --> 00:58:42,520
I have to do better,
for everybody.

748
00:58:42,600 --> 00:58:44,040
Except me.

749
00:58:44,120 --> 00:58:45,560
Except you.

750
00:58:46,680 --> 00:58:50,400
Well, I hope you can.
I think you will.

751
00:58:51,400 --> 00:58:53,680
You're doing the right thing.

752
00:59:08,160 --> 00:59:10,800
Who knows what's
going to happen, Duffy?

753
00:59:10,880 --> 00:59:12,600
I'll probably see you tomorrow.

754
00:59:54,640 --> 00:59:56,200
Get out of my chimney.

755
00:59:56,320 --> 00:59:57,480
Listen to me.

756
00:59:57,560 --> 01:00:00,600
