and extreme high waters.

1064
01:24:03,840 --> 01:24:07,760
On St. Jack Wood,
powerful surges broke the arcade boardwalk

1065
01:24:07,880 --> 01:24:11,160
and demolished
the village bandstand and casino.

1066
01:24:12,200 --> 01:24:14,800
Scout Master's log.
October 10th.

1067
01:24:14,880 --> 01:24:17,560
Reconstruction continues
increasingly ahead of schedule,

1068
01:24:18,120 --> 01:24:20,160
which I attribute to
a particularly robust

1069
01:24:20,240 --> 01:24:22,080
esprit de corps
among the troop.

1070
01:24:22,160 --> 01:24:23,360
The latrine, however,
does continue to present...

1071
01:24:23,440 --> 01:24:24,560
Excuse me, sir?

1072
01:24:24,640 --> 01:24:26,600
- You've got the new recruit?
- Yes, sir.

1073
01:24:26,680 --> 01:24:28,200
- What's his rank?
- He doesn't have one.

1074
01:24:28,280 --> 01:24:29,960
Pigeon Scout.
Let's get him a patch.

1075
01:24:30,040 --> 01:24:31,960
The coastal
areas of New Penzance

1076
01:24:32,040 --> 01:24:34,000
were battered
and changed forever.

1077
01:24:34,080 --> 01:24:35,640
Height.

1078
01:24:36,520 --> 01:24:37,720
63 inches.

1079
01:24:38,280 --> 01:24:41,120
Mile 3.25
Tidal Inlet was erased from the map.

1080
01:24:43,120 --> 01:24:45,040
But harvest yields
the following autumn

1081
01:24:45,120 --> 01:24:47,800
far exceeded any
previously recorded,

1082
01:24:48,720 --> 01:24:52,480
and the quality of the crops
was said to be extraordinary.

1083
01:24:58,760 --> 01:25:01,360
So you see,
the composer Benjamin Britten

1084
01:25:01,440 --> 01:25:03,920
