back together again in a fugue.

1086
01:25:07,000 --> 01:25:08,800
The instruments come
in one after another

1087
01:25:08,920 --> 01:25:12,160
in the same order as before,
beginning with the piccolo.

1088
01:25:12,240 --> 01:25:15,360
And at the end, when all the
instruments have finally come in...

1089
01:25:15,480 --> 01:25:17,920
Suzy, Lionel,
Murray, Rudy, dinner!

1090
01:25:18,000 --> 01:25:19,400
Melody, while
the other instruments...

